Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.card

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Card
    Abstract class containing the victory points.
    Deck
    Represent the set of leader cards and the set of development cards, divided in smaller decks as the game specifies.
    DevelopmentCard
    Subclass that models a DevelopmentCard.
    LeaderCard
    Subclass that models a leader card.
    LeaderCardRequirement
    Models requirements for leader cards, as they can be resources or development cards.
    SpecialAbility
    Models a special ability, storing the type and the target resource.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    CardColor
    An enumeration containing the possible card colors.
    SpecialAbilityType
    Represents the four types of special abilities for leader cards.
